Short Term - 
- Temp disable View Changelog button
- Remove the cents from the admin panel proposal view and designer proposal view
- Custom Tile, Coping, Decking with inputs for total cost - replaces pre selected option in costs
Were going to include a new option in the dropdown menus of the Tle Level, Coping Type, and Decking Type dropdowns inside of the Tile / Coping / Decking category. Include an option for "No Tile" in the Tile Level, "No Coping" in the Coping Type, and "No Decking" in the Decking Type. Selecting one of these options will remove the costs associated with selecting a level of tile, coping, and decking. Essentially letting the pool designer skip that portion if it is not needed for this build. 
