Mid Term - 
- $$ Logo upload option for admin, makes available for franchise
Inside of the Settings panel if an Admin / Owner is signed in, a new setting allowing the upload/input of a Global Logo to be used by the Franchise the Admin is apart of. If an Admin inputs a logo into this new area, the default Submerge logo that is used throughout the App will be replaced by the logo that the Admin provides for their franchise. Be thorough and detailed when determining where this logo swap will occur, it should be everywhere inside of the App that would normally have the Submerge logo or need a logo. This new logo will reflect for all of the designers /adminds in that particular franchise as well. 
- Login passwords and role promotion / pass reset
