- Homescreen UI update for designers
We need to make some changes with the way a designer sees the Homescreen. Remove the Performance Overview entirly, and leave just the Recent Proposals and Quick Actions blocks. Next, in the Proposals tab, remove the Total Cogs, Gross Profit %, and Gross Profit Amount columns from view. Add a new column named "Proposal Versions" listing how many versions the proposal has. This column should be listed after the Pricing Model column. Then, add another new column named "Contract Type" and list the type of contract that the proposal applies to - NC Guntie, NC Fiberglass, SC Gunite, SC Fiberglass. The Retail Price should be the last column.

